                <h2 class="txt-black">The Maverick Awards Categories</h2>
                <p>The sectoral development categories are a reflection of the priority sectors of our economy as outlined in our National Development Plan, that have been dentified as important drivers for our future economic growth and job creation endeavours. The intention is to create a pipeline for the development of these industries, by using The Maverick Awards to identify and recognise young entrepreneurs that display high impact - high growth potential in these sectors 
in order for developmental interventions to be awarded to their businesses through The Maverick Awards so they may grow quicker, from micro to small, small to medium, medium to large players and therefore catalyse their ability to effectively and sustainably contribute towards employment creation and economic growth.</p>
