<p class="sub-prof-head txt-gold"><b>The Maverick Recognition Award Categories</b></p>
<p>These categories are a new and exciting addition to The Maverick Awards; they have been created to recognise the contribution made by exceptional young entrepreneurs based on their businesses size, revenue generation and proven employment creation.  Each of the sectoral award category entrants would have an opportunity to enter at least one or a maximum of two recognition awards depending on the nature of their businesses and businesses size.</p>
